1368
01:53:41,031 --> 01:53:44,059
And you gotta do the job on her,
Charley.

1369
01:53:44,167 --> 01:53:47,520
You're the only one who can get
close enough to do it.

1370
01:53:48,406 --> 01:53:50,137
Zip Irene?

1371
01:53:51,369 --> 01:53:52,948
Clip Irene?

