1375
01:54:00,367 --> 01:54:02,076
maybe even to the chair.

1376
01:54:02,985 --> 01:54:06,143
Filargi will go free and
we'll never get the bank.

1377
01:54:06,272 --> 01:54:07,895
There's no choice here.

1378
01:54:12,221 --> 01:54:15,538
How is doing a number on Irene
gonna satisfy the cops...

1379
01:54:15,638 --> 01:54:17,715
about the broad that pushed
the wrong button?

1380
01:54:19,358 --> 01:54:22,262
