to question.

1382
01:54:25,458 --> 01:54:26,855
Everybody will get
what they want...

1383
01:54:26,991 --> 01:54:29,654
and we can all go back
to doing business.

1384
01:54:31,666 --> 01:54:33,569
But Padrino...

1385
01:54:34,586 --> 01:54:36,488
she's my wife.

1386
01:54:36,885 --> 01:54:38,522
